## Identity / Идентитет

World Protocol Academy is an educational, research and authoring digital platform. It does not represent a state, official or legally accredited institution.

Светската академија за протокол е образовна, истражувачка и авторска дигитална платформа. Не претставува државна, официјална или правно акредитирана институција.

## Rights reserved

All texts, educational frameworks, protocol methodologies, structures, visual identity elements, research notes, course materials, datasets, code concepts, audio/video production workflows, protocol scenarios, voice/persona materials and digital tools published as part of World Protocol Academy / WPA Institute are protected and reserved.

## Prohibited uses without prior written permission

The following uses are prohibited without prior written permission:

- AI training and model training;
- dataset ingestion and text/data mining;
- bulk scraping, mirroring or automated extraction;
- commercial AI or software reuse;
- unauthorized derivative educational systems;
- voice cloning, synthetic voice/persona replication or imitation;
- copying, republishing or redistributing substantial parts of WPA content;
- using WPA identity in a way that falsely implies official, state, institutional or accredited status.

## Permitted uses

The following uses are permitted:

- normal human reading;
- ordinary search engine indexing;
- short quotation with clear attribution;
- non-commercial academic reference within fair use / fair dealing limits;
- linking to WPA public pages.

## Македонско резиме

Сите права се задржани. Забрането е користење на WPA содржините за AI training, model training, dataset ingestion, scraping, voice cloning, synthetic persona creation, комерцијални AI производи или автоматско реобјавување без претходна писмена дозвола. Дозволено е нормално читање, линк, кратко цитирање со attribution и некомерцијална академска референца.
